<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>87</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Hallellujah Lalpa lopi pen,
 A pakna la'n gamtin thawng hen;
 Namtin Lal lopi leh zahum pen chun,
 Mi lunggil sungah thu hun gen kit hen.

[V2]
 Hun pui kitin aw taimang sate,
 Ipmute chu phawng halh kit inla;
 Khawvel puipa Aksi lopipen,
 Manna gam leh lungzinna gam salhvak in.

[V3]
 2. Lal David leh puihuoi muonum Mosi,
 Lei aksi lien a tum zo tau;
 Tuhin Lal Krista leh Thagau Thiengtho,
 I thiempuu Lalpen leh I Aksiu chu.

[V4]
 3. Tui leh sietlei him him a um manle,
 Het phak loh Pathien na hi ie;
 Ni leh tha leh aksihaw cheng cheng khun,
 Nang vangin vakna lopi a nei ui.

[V5]
 4. Thuneihna chungnung chawihatna sangpen,
 Vangletna nei tak Na hi ie;
 Sietlei um tunga thahsa Belam No,
 A thisan lunin khawvel hukdam hen.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Hallelujah !</title>
</song>